<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>물품 등록/수정 - MediCare+</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script src="/js/feather.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
  
  {{> components/sidebar}}

  <div class="main-content">
    {{> components/header}}
    
    <main class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600">
              <i data-feather="package" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">{{#item}}물품 정보 수정{{/item}}{{^item}}물품 등록{{/item}}</h1>
              <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">병원에서 사용하는 물품의 재고와 최소 수량을 관리합니다.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/items" class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-700">
            목록으로 돌아가기
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-8">
          <form action="{{#item}}/items/{{id}}/update{{/item}}{{^item}}/items/create{{/item}}" method="POST" class="space-y-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">물품명</label>
                <div class="relative">
                  <i data-feather="package" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                  <input type="text" name="name" value="{{#item}}{{name}}{{/item}}" required class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 outline-none" placeholder="예: 알코올 솜"/>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">카테고리</label>
                <div class="relative">
                  <i data-feather="layers" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                  <select name="category" required class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 focus:border-indigo-500 outline-none bg-white">
                    <option value="의료소모품" {{#isMedical}}selected{{/isMedical}}>의료소모품</option>
                    <option value="의약품" {{#isDrug}}selected{{/isDrug}}>의약품</option>
                    <option value="사무용품" {{#isOffice}}selected{{/isOffice}}>사무용품</option>
                    <option value="기타비품" {{#isEtc}}selected{{/isEtc}}>기타비품</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">현재 재고 수량</label>
                <div class="relative">
                  <i data-feather="hash" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                  <input type="number" name="stock" value="{{#item}}{{stock}}{{/item}}" required min="0" class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none"/>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">최소 유지 수량</label>
                <div class="relative">
                  <i data-feather="hash" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-5 h-5 text-slate-400"></i>
                  <input type="number" name="minStock" value="{{#item}}{{minStock}}{{/item}}" required min="0" class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none"/>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-slate-700 mb-2">단위</label>
                <input type="text" name="unit" value="{{#item}}{{unit}}{{/item}}" required class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-slate-300 rounded-xl focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500 outline-none" placeholder="예: 개, 박스, 정"/>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-200 flex justify-end gap-3">
              <a href="/items" class="px-6 py-3 bg-white border border-slate-300 text-slate-700 font-medium rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">취소</a>
              <button type="submit" class="px-8 py-3 bg-indigo-600 text-white font-medium rounded-xl hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors shadow-sm flex items-center gap-2">
                <i data-feather="save" class="w-5 h-5"></i> 저장하기
              </button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    {{> components/footer}}
  </div>

  <script>
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
      feather.replace();
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>